Package: refverifier
Type: Package
Title: Reference Verifier for Scientific Citations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Salvatore
Maintainer: Salvatore <your-email@example.com>
Description: Parses plain-text bibliographic references and verifies them
    using Crossref, OpenAlex, and additional metadata checks.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr, purrr, tibble, readr, stringi, stringdist, httr, jsonlite, stringr, gt
